<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title><%= subject %></title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #dc3545;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
            border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;
        }
        .logo {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            border: 1px solid #e9e9e9;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px;
            border: 1px solid #e9e9e9;
            border-top: none;
        }
        .order-details {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid #e9e9e9;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .detail-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 8px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
        }
        .detail-row:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .shipping-block {
            margin-top: 20px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border: 2px dashed #dc3545;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .highlight {
            color: #dc3545;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .steps {
            margin: 20px 0;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }
        .steps li {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #dc3545;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .social-links {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        .social-links a {
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 0 10px;
            color: #666;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <div class="logo">
            <img src="https://static.wixstatic.com/media/bb6757_10a18cb451534e60a77f266c95fa3657~mv2.jpg" alt="Spectra Metals Logo" width="120">
        </div>
        <h1>Your Metal Selling Request</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <p>Dear <%= order.name %>,</p>
        
        <p>Thank you for choosing to sell your metals with Spectra Metal Transactions. We have received your request and are waiting for your shipment.</p>
        
        <div class="order-details">
            <h3>Transaction Details</h3>
            <div class="detail-row">
                <strong>Reference Number:</strong>
                <span><%= order.orderNumber %></span>
            </div>
            <div class="detail-row">
                <strong>Date:</strong>
                <span><%= new Date(order.createdAt).toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' }) %></span>
            </div>
            <div class="detail-row">
                <strong>Metal:</strong>
                <span><%= order.metal %></span>
            </div>
            <div class="detail-row">
                <strong>Weight:</strong>
                <span><%= order.grams %> grams</span>
            </div>
            <div class="detail-row">
                <strong>Offered Price:</strong>
                <span><%= order.calculatedPrice %></span>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <h3>Next Steps</h3>
        <ol class="steps">
            <li>Package your metal securely.</li>
            <li>Include a printed copy of this email or a note with your reference number <span class="highlight"><%= order.orderNumber %></span>.</li>
            <li>Ship your package to the address below.</li>
            <li>Once we receive and verify your metals, we'll process your payment within 3-5 business days.</li>
            <li>You'll receive payment confirmation via email.</li>
        </ol>
        
        <div class="shipping-block">
            <h3 style="color: #dc3545; text-align: center; margin-top: 0;">SHIPPING ADDRESS</h3>
            <p style="text-align: center;">
                Spectra Metal Transactions<br>
                123 Metal Street<br>
                New York, NY 10001<br>
                United States
            </p>
            <p style="text-align: center;">
                <strong>Important:</strong> Please include your reference number <span class="highlight"><%= order.orderNumber %></span> with your shipment.
            </p>
        </div>
        
        <% if (order.receiptUrl) { %>
            <p>You can view and download your receipt by clicking the button below:</p>
            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="<%= order.receiptUrl %>" class="button" target="_blank">View Receipt</a>
            </div>
        <% } %>
        
        <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to contact our customer support at <a href="mailto:support@spectra.com">support@spectra.com</a> or call us at +1 (555) 123-4567.</p>
        
        <p>Thank you for choosing Spectra Metal Transactions!</p>
        
        <p>Best Regards,<br>
        The Spectra Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Spectra Metal Transactions. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>123 Metal Street, New York, NY 10001</p>
        <div class="social-links">
            <a href="#">Facebook</a> | <a href="#">Twitter</a> | <a href="#">Instagram</a> | <a href="#">LinkedIn</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>